FPGA Architecture Parameters
- Fixed layout (WxH), channel width
- LUT size (k6N10)

Soft-core Design Parameters
- PicoRV32, VexRiscv, IBEX, ...
- Core ISA RV32 (I, IM, IMC)
- Memory cache size ($I + $D)
- Clock period
